sellerCard.oneLiner: Get Laravel Development Services That Surpasses Your Expectations
sellerCard.description:
I am a full-stack PHP Laravel Developer who can cater to your website and web application needs. I have been in this industry for over 6 years, supervised the production department of a famous software company, and catered to various freelance web application orders.

I have an experience in:
·         HTML
·         CSS
·         DB Design
·         Real-Time Pushes
·         API Documentation
·         Middlewares
·         Real-time chat systems
·         Website Development

Just send me a message, and let me make these complex things a piece of cake for you!

description.content:
Are you seeking a full-stack PHP developer with over 6 years of experience in web development, specializing in PHP/Laravel? Look no further! I'm here to assist you with a wide range of services, including:


  • Building new web applications
  • Integrating APIs
  • Bug fixing and maintenance
  • Designing and developing responsive websites
  • Collaborating closely with you to deliver high-quality results


My Skill Set Includes:


  • HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap
  • Laravel
  • MySQL / Database
  • PHP
  • JavaScript, jQuery, Ajax
  • CRUD operations
  • Development from scratch
  • Cron job implementation
  • Google API integration
  • GitHub version control
  • Laravel web application development and customization
  • Adding new features and social media login
  • API development
  • Laravel bug fixing
  • Payment gateway integration (PayPal, Stripe, etc.)


Why choose me?


  • Reliable Communication
  • On- Time delivery
  • Reasonable Prices
  • Customer Satisfaction
  • High- Quality Results


Ready to elevate your web presence with a custom PHP Laravel solution? Contact me now to discuss your project requirements and get started on building something amazing together.

questionsAndAnswers.question: My required services are not listed in your Gig; can I share my task?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I have done Laravel and web application projects of various famous companies across the UK, USA and Australia and if you have a customized order, do not worry I will do it flawlessly!

questionsAndAnswers.question: I want to make an online voting system for my company, can you develop it?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely, as an experienced PHP Laravel Developer, I can certainly make it!

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I did not like your work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: If you have ordered the work that has not surpassed your expectations, I will revise it, until you are 100% satisfied.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why do I need a PHP Laravel Developer?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: As a PHP Laravel Developer, I can design websites and assist you with web applications. As an experienced professional, I can ensure everything is correct and done in less time.

questionsAndAnswers.question: As a Laravel Developer, do you work on e-commerce website projects?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can design them to make them user-friendly and able to handle high traffic.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I have four different projects; I need static, single-page (SPA), multi-page (MPA), dynamic, and portal web applications; do you know about them?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, these all are the services that I have experienced over 6 years and can certainly assist you! I can develop any of your required page and website just discuss it with me.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I need someone to debug and code fix my website; if you can handle it, how much will you charge?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, as a PHP developer, I can easily do your work, and the charges are according to the project. I need to see the website first, but do not worry; I will never overcharge you!

reviews.comment: I had an incredible experience working with Habib Noor! From user registration for individuals and businesses to a lead management system, comparison tool, payment gateway integration, and even real-time chat, every feature was implemented flawlessly. What truly impressed me was his attention to detail, ensuring GDPR compliance and data security while optimizing the platform for both mobile and desktop. The level of professionalism, skill, and dedication Habib brought to this project was remarkable.

There are no words to describe this project. It was so well done. I will tell him in three words.

Laravel Expert
Professional
Affordable

That's all.

Keep it up, bro.

seller_response.comment: Thanks for your feedback. Looking forward to working with you on your further projects.

reviews.comment: Habib is a skilled and professional developer with a polite and collaborative approach. He supported my team through a challenging project and was an invaluable asset. I highly recommend him without hesitation!!!

seller_response.comment: Thank you so much for your support throughout!
